output:
Map {
  User Stories {
    Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the Horses application.
    Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select the travel time for my horse.
    View Horse Details: As a user, I want to be able to view the details of a horse, such as its breed, age, and health.
    Book Horse: As a user, I want to be able to book a horse for a specific time and date.
    View Horse History: As a user, I want to be able to view the history of a horse, such as its past owners and races.
    Manage Horse: As a user, I want to be able to manage a horse, such as feeding, grooming, and training.
    View Horse Performance: As a user, I want to be able to view the performance of a horse, such as its speed and agility.
    Track Horse: As a user, I want to be able to track a horse, such as its location and activity.
  }
  User Interface {
    Login Page: As a user, I want to be able to log in to the Horses application.
    Home Page: As a user, I want to be able to view the home page of the Horses application.
    Horse List Page: As a user, I want to be able to view a list of horses available for booking.
    Horse Details Page: As a user, I want to be able to view the details of a horse.
    Booking Page: As a user, I want to be able to book a horse for a specific time and date.
    History Page: As a user, I want to be able to view the history of a horse.
    Performance Page: As a user, I want to be able to view the performance of a horse.
    Tracking Page: As a user, I want to be able to track a horse.
  }
}
